  <p align="left">    The MLT, after discussion with the Board, would like to propose a change to the way YFC operates its mission giving.</p>
  <p><strong>Currently</strong></p>
  <p>Each YFC centre contributes a monthly amount which goes into a missions fund. The amounts given are:</p>
