  </table>
  <p>This giving results as a total of around $24,000.00 per year which is given to overseas YFC projects, and other missionaries with which YFC has contact.</p>
  <p><strong>The challenge</strong></p>
  <p>The existing quota amounts were decided years ago and don't really represent what's going on in local areas anymore. And under the new value of generosity the MLT and Board believe there's a better way that gives all YFC members the chance to take on the responsibility.</p>
  <p><strong>Proposal</strong></p>
  <p>That the members in each local area get together and decide how much they would like to contribute collectively from their area. The current monthly contribution will end this month (November). We would like an indication by December, of a new amount. You could choose to give the same, less, or more. You could do it as a one off, or continue a monthly payment.</p>
  <p>When we have the commitments from every area, we'll know how much we can give away during 2007. At the ethos weekends in February, members will have a chance to decide how the money is dispersed.</p>
  <p>Feel free to contact any one of us if you want more information.</p>
